                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Indexing",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Evaluate and implement appropriate indexing strategies on the join and filter columns to improve performance."
